{"tid":2360098,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：閘機人咁高 水馬變花槽  保安升級 立會變監獄（李八方）","createTime":"2021-01-09T12:10:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T12:10:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2418d04af12e81927a2191f4544e7d152825ccc9","tid":2360098,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T12:10:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/77LO4GFDKNFGBHXKBJGIY5KB4U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2F77LO4GFDKNFGBHXKBJGIY5KB4U%2F&d=3UqZ%2FPYEUq8PtOmaimGdDYvgSq%2BgcR%2FX%2FBaLnjou7zI%3D&h=f316d07d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210108%2F77LO4GFDKNFGBHXKBJGIY5KB4U%2F&h=45b9d86e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210108/77LO4GFDKNFGBHXKBJGIY5KB4U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：閘機人咁高 水馬變花槽 <br />\n保安升級 立會變監獄（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fdJh4f-as16yeXmBlbj3QAw5xtw=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MAK46V6HZ5C3TBZ7KIEBJNPIZ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfdJh4f-as16yeXmBlbj3QAw5xtw%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMAK46V6HZ5C3TBZ7KIEBJNPIZ4.jpg&h=f7781ab6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n設計圖片<br />\n<br />\n自從抗爭者前年7.1衝入立法會後，建制派一直要求要加強立法會保安，去年9月行管會就落實保安專家建議，喺立法會大樓一樓同二樓電梯位置，分別加裝1.8米高嘅閘機，加強出入管制，最近有關設施陸續動工，部份更已出現喺大樓入面，但有議員睇到就覺得，呢啲所謂「保安設施」令人覺得好似起緊監獄咁。<br />\n<br />\n喺眾多加強立法會保安設施入面，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/t5pQHYRuzw4fc8GrsWfFe6Cf-Cc=/1181x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/76355UYJHVCAHEPHALF7VTHV2U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ft5pQHYRuzw4fc8GrsWfFe6Cf-Cc%3D%2F1181x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F76355UYJHVCAHEPHALF7VTHV2U.jpg&h=891cd5ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■現時喺立法會外嘅水馬陣動工變成永久嘅圍欄同花槽。鄭松泰提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/e-5OOpcKtp8_t2cL-85e0jnagy8=/827x529/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2PB5KPVDCJFCZC7X2JKYBT3VLU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fe-5OOpcKtp8_t2cL-85e0jnagy8%3D%2F827x529%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2PB5KPVDCJFCZC7X2JKYBT3VLU.jpg&h=76d30a0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■立法會地下入口裝好多部閘機，每部連膠板都有1.8米高。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n泰博質疑浪費公帑<br />\n<br />\n除咗裝新入閘機，其實行管會當時亦通過其他措施增強保安，包括將現時喺立法會外嘅水馬陣，由臨時水馬變成永久性嘅圍欄同花槽，而且已經動工，只係仲未完成。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n李八方"}]}